Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless pirates fight\Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the great treasure left behind\Nby Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body\Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,also takes to the sea\Nto become the next Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As Luffy and his friends\Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the World Government is less and less\Nable to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What adventure is waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe Paramount War against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy made it to Maiden Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,where he was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy has been left with Dadan - \Nthe mountain bandit of Mt. Corvo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and met 2 precocious kids named Ace and Sabo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with whom he pledged to be brothers forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Our brotherhood will always be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,we're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become a pirate before \Nyou do so just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair! I'm gonna \Nbecome a pirate first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still saying a crap like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you both understand that \Nyou must become Navy soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"We will stand on our feet."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are!
