Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Seasons come and go and now it's winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo! He's coming to you! \NDon't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! We drove him to the bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We got two of them today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have a lot of danpa soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I did it! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a kill for the first time! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, watch your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A big tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He caught wind of our prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, get away from there! \NHe just wants the danpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my prize! I'm not gonna let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...h-h-have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too tough for you! Get away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Go away, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'm gonna beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--That fool!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run while he's distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get even with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about your first prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone. We had no \Nchance against that tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was my prize! \NHe can't just steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You fool! Don't shake it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--You little...!\N--Stop, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo! Pull us up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home finally! Let's just \Ngo to bed on such a bad day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to bed on a bad day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's your fault!\N--Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But if someone steals the prize you \Ncaught by yourself for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why someone would get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--But it's reckless to fight such a big tiger...\N--That's something you would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:10:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great to have brothers! \NIf they come aboard my ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, you keep out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll fight too because I'm a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna make your stomach full.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Sabo! You guys gotta come \Naboard my ship! Okay? Say yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to leave it to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'd be fun to be with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll need my help, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who needs help, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are welcome to come aboard my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--No, my ship!\N--No, my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this is not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,--Are you sure about it?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna work for anyone. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! It's gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who beats the big \Ntiger can be the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The big tiger? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The chances of you becoming \Na captain are pretty low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! None of us \Ncan compete against him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,--Good idea!\N--Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,--Alright!\N--Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We went through so much to \Ncatch these. What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain. We caught \Nthese to use them as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? There he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a greedy bastard! \NHe can't have them today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! It's a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what we expected! \NGo away! Shoo! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it seems like he's \Nas strong as the tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't beat the tiger if we can't beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So he's perfect for practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--I go first!\N--That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! He's not cooling off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He better run - that old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Naguri from Gray Terminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! He's coming to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that you don't belong here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to the forest now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that time before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You were a pirate \Nand a captain, Naguri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Only a pirate \Ncaptain could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"That"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You made the big bear turn away \Njust by staring at him like Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cool, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that Naguri \Nwas a pirate because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always collecting junk, hammering \Naway at them all day long,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,making weird stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting teased by the people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,at Gray Terminal and by Bluejam's crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know nothing, Sabo! \NThat's how pirates are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know pirates! Shanks doesn't \Ndo needless killings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanks, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ow, ow, ow...!\N--Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you got more than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some, Naguri. You helped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is a pirate captain \Ndoing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you ask me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to answer \Nif you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know Gold Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know him! He was the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We challenged Roger, the Pirate King, to a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But we lost the fight and split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything just went downhill after that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's basically what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you fought with the Pirate King, right? That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, we were no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:18:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We got beaten badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Even you were no \Nmatch - that's how much he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And not just Roger, his \Ncrew was also very strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Most importantly, their teamwork \Nwas in perfect coordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was our honor to fight with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! I still have a long \Nway to go to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you interested in pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm gonna become one!\N--Become a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a pirate! Oh yeah, old pirate \Nman, could you give me some tips?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to become a captain \Nto lead Ace and Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, say yes! You're a pirate master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--Okay!\N--Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Then, let's start from tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Ace go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pirate King is his father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But you can't tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it to Ace. He's gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why but he \Ndoesn't like Roger for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's his father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for both of you but I was \Nall by myself even if I had parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Your parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Children don't always get \Nalong with their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what a shame! He's \Nthe Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand that you \Nwanna ask him about Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but just don't, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And... you too, Naguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't believe that \Nthat boy is Roger's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is. Hey, just act casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't mention...\N--I know! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ace! I didn't know that you were home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ace! I didn't know that \Nyour father was Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he'd say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, Luffy! I told \Nyou to not to mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Ace, what was Roger like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid are you? Don't \Njust say it casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! I am acting casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ouch!\N--Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever mention \Nthat name when I'm around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you hit me?! \NDon't be mean - just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Give people a chance to explain first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us about him! You're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! You can't have \Na secret from your brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I don't care about my brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, Roger, Roger! Ace's father \Nis the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't provoke him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get down to it, it's \Nyour fault for being a bigmouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're no longer brothers from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--That's what I was gonna say!\N--That's what I was gonna say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll leave no stone unturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but if you find him, \Ndon't do anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.59,0:22:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see? We have to make \Nhis father feel indebted to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The longer he worries, the more he'll \Nappreciate us when we find Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.83,0:22:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the time comes, don't do \Nanything - just monitor him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"We will have a visit this spring"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogra! Magra! Where is \Nthe country called Goa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Corvo, Gray Terminal, \Nand Windmill Village
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,are part of Goa Kingdom supposedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to see you reading a \Nnewspaper. Hell must be freezing over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:22:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's gonna visit the Kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's making the headlines...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here? \NAre they that big a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.41,0:23:14.04,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Celestial Dragon Visiting"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,These Celestial Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious after Luffy is taken in as an \Napprentice, Ace and Sabo visit Naguri again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing that the boys only care about \Ngetting strong enough to beat a tiger,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Naguri tells them that they can't become \Npirate captains just by being strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it really take \Nto be a pirate captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Battle Against the Big Tiger! \NWho's Going to be Captain?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
